name: ArtisanTheory
description:
ArtisanTheory

ArtisanTheory is a mix and match of Many Models as well as some of my personally trained LoRA.

Speaking of, I would advise against using my Seasons, Khyle., and SydusArt LoRA as they may create a messy output (You could still use them, but at a low weighting to enhance the styles already present).

I find that it is very easy to make great looking images with this Model, especially in terms of the colour strength, as well as the dynamic posing that has been derived from my Khyle. LoRA.

Understand that there is a character style that comes with this Model, as well as some character that you wont find in others.

Can quite often have intrusive characters when you are only wanting 1. Feel free to use tags such as solo, solo focus, male focus, female focus.

Enjoy!
